text:
Date of visit: Tue 21 Nov 2023
Time : 7.15 pm

Long time never been back here. This time tried the curry fish head. Priced at $29 and 2 rice at $0.80 each

Big portion and Fish is good. So are the brinjal, lady fingers, tomatoes, tau pok and tau kee.

The curry is flavorful and tasty.
This tzechar is not bad. Recommend their cury fish head and Nonya style spicy fish head. Ask for more gravy, guaranteed to top up rice lol.
Auntie always very stingy to give chilli. 2packs chilli is very big deal for themüòÖ

Must-try their prawn fried rice
Nice üëçüëçüëç
After eating their prawn fried rice will never eat other stores fried rice anymore
Favorite dish here got to be their patong fish head and the pork ribs king. Do give their other dishes a try too.
